<?php 
switch($verse){
case 1:{?>When the hypocrites come unto thee ( O Muhammad ), they say : We bear witness that thou art indeed Allah ' s messenger. And Allah knoweth that thou art indeed His messenger, and Allah beareth witness that the Hypocrites are speaking falsely.<?php break;}
case 2:{?>They make their faith a pretext that they may turn ( men ) from the way of Allah. Verily evil is that which they are wont to do,<?php break;}
case 3:{?>That is because they believed, then disbelieved, therefore their hearts are sealed so that they understand not.<?php break;}
case 4:{?>And when thou seest them their figures please thee; and if they speak thou givest ear unto their speech. ( They are ) as though they were blocks of wood in striped cloaks. They deem every shout to be against them. They are the enemy, so beware of them. Allah confound them! How they are perverted!<?php break;}
case 5:{?>And when it is said unto them : Come! The messenger of Allah will ask forgiveness for you! they avert their faces and thou seest them turning away, disdainful.<?php break;}
case 6:{?>Whether thou ask forgiveness for them or ask not forgiveness for them, Allah will not forgive them. Lo! Allah guideth not the evil living folk.<?php break;}
case 7:{?>They it is who say : Spend not on behalf of those ( who dwell ) with Allah ' s messenger that they may disperse ( and go away from you ); when Allah ' s are the treasures of the heavens and the earth; but the hypocrites comprehend not.<?php break;}
case 8:{?>They say : Surely, if we return to Al Madinah the mightier will soon drive out the weaker; when might belongeth to Allah and to His messenger and the believers; but the hypocrites know not.<?php break;}
case 9:{?>O ye who believe! Let not your wealth nor your children distract you from remembrance of Allah. Those who do so, they are the losers.<?php break;}
case 10:{?>And spend of that wherewith We have provided you before death cometh unto one of you and he saith : My Lord! If only thou wouldst reprieve me for a little while, then I would give alms and be among the righteous.<?php break;}
case 11:{?>But Allah reprieveth no soul when its term cometh, and Allah is Aware of what ye do.<?php break;}
